title: Bag making machine for vest and flat bags (2 layer) US-DZB-800
title_uz: Maykali va oddiy paket ishlab chiqaish uskunasi (2 qavatli) US-DZB-800
title_ru: Машина для изготовления пакетов «майка» и плоских пакетов (2 слоя) US-DZB-800
title_en: Bag making machine for vest and flat bags (2 layer) US-DZB-800
short_description: This US-DZB-800 model equipment is suitable for the production of both "t-shirt" shaped and plain bags. The equipment has a production capacity of 40-120 pieces/min*2, the total power is 5 kW, the weight of the equipment is 1000 kg, and the size is 3.3 * 1.4 * 1.5 m. There are other models of this equipment in the description, and their prices differed from each other.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-DZB-800 modeldagi uskuna ham mayka shaklidagi, ham oddiy paket ishlab chiqarish uchun moslashgan. Uskuna donasiga 40-120 dona/min*2 ishlab chiqarish quvvatiga ega, umumiy quvvati 5 kW, uskuna vazni 1000 kg va o'lchami esa 3.3 * 1.4 * 1.5 m. Tavsifda bu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham mavjud va ularning narxlari bir-biridan farqlanadi.
